data.description: This beautiful 3 story home is located in historic North East Kansas City. It was rehabbed about 2 years ago.  Updates include Kitchen granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, bathrooms, interior paint, electrical, plumbing, HVAC, doors, windows, carpet, refinished hardwood floors, exterior paint and siding. Home has five bedrooms, 3 baths.  The 5th bedroom is on the 3rd floor.  The 1st floor has an office with a full bath that could also be used as a bedroom.
